#This readme shows how to run these programs.
#'>' means the start of the commandline in Unix system.

1. Sobel Edge Detection

>python sobel.py [original filename] [generated filename]

ex.
>python sobel.py test.tif sobel_test.png


2. Mean Filtering

>python mean_3.py [original filename] [generated filename]
>python mean_5.py [original filename] [generated filename]

3. Median Filtering
>python median.py [original filename] [generated filename]

4. Laplace Filtering
>python laplace.py [original filename] [generated filename]

5. Otsu Filtering
>python otsu.py [original filename] [generated filename]
